pr_title: Rework of CSRs according to the specs
pr_body:
This PR is a collection of commits that focus on updating the SupRegFile to reflect the ISA specifications.
I used the RISC-V privileged ISA specification, Document Version 20211203, Supervisor ISA 1.12.
The PR contains:

- new CSR in the SupRegFile according to the specs
- tracking of current privilege level, changing at trap entry, and trap return (M, S, U mode)
- addition of missing instructions: MRET, FENCE.I
- fix to correctly execute SH
